channel.title: People cant log on to my server now
channel.description:
Everyone could log onto my server yesterday and today but now they can't for some reason now. They get error connecting to server. I didn't touch port forward thing. But I don't have static IP becuse my ISP won't let me. Could that be why? if it is how do i fix?
EDIT: do you think someone might have crashed server?

item.title: People cant log on to my server now
item.dc:creator: @raped_by_who raped by who
item.description:
@raped_by_who wrote:

Cuban0 Ftw:

Static IP simply means your IP changes everyday. It may be the problem, if someone crashed your server then it would be on 3-5min maybe less.

Actually… DYNAMIC IP changes every time.
Static is permanent.
